# Test API Calls for Property System
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@userToken = YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Check Database Status (Admin required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/seed-all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Seed All Data (Admin required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/seed-all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get All Properties (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties

### Get Properties by Type - Single
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties?type=single

### Get Properties by Type - Project  
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties?type=project

### Get Properties by Type - Bundle
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties?type=bundle

### Get Featured Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties/featured

### Search Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties/search?q=villa

### Filter Properties by Price Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties?minPrice=1000000&maxPrice=5000000

### Filter Properties by ROI
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties?minRoi=15&maxRoi=25

### Filter Available Properties Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties?available=true

### Get Property Details (replace with actual property ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties/PROPERTY_ID_HERE

### Calculate Investment (replace with actual property ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/properties/PROPERTY_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shares": 5
}

### Get User Investments (User authentication required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/investments
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Create Investment (User authentication required, replace with actual property ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/investments
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "propertyId": "PROPERTY_ID_HERE",
  "sharesInvested": 3
}

### Get Payment Schedule (User authentication required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/investments/payments?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Admin - Get All Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin - Get Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Owner - Get My Properties (Owner authentication required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/owner/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
